Development Roadmap for 1.2.x
-----------------------------
Version: $Id$

C = Committed

1.2.8
        Small enchancement patches
        'Other' arch fixes as and when tested
        #1205 - Add debug option to SystemLog
        #1241 - Homedir on demand
        #1272 - DenyFilter by User or DenyFilter by Dire
        #1403 - per-server system logs via ServerLog directive
        #1482 - %U cookie to LogFormat
        #1507 - regex pattern matching in [Allow/Deny][User/Group]
        #1515 - Enable mod_log to log into default log / syslog
        #1565 - ftpwho bandwidth usage
        #1597 - Problems with HP-UX 10/11 trusted systems, mod_pam, and mod_unixpw
        #1605 - MKD and RMD do not log filepaths
        #1653 - Complete the FS API abstraction implementation
        #1671 - new directive SQLLogFile
        #1705 - Add contrib module for time-of-day restrictions
        #1712 - TLS support
        #1743 - No magic cookie for number of files transferred
        #1767 - Reporting problem with ftpwho (transfer rate)
        #1788 - Add ability to configure auth module checking order
        #1789 - Add ability to block recursive directory options
        #1806 - Add RFC2389 support 
        #1825 - AUTH macro namespace cleanup
        #1833 - Add ability to have add'l module initialization callback

1.2.9
